{"tid":1031264,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔眼中既仆街行業入面有邊d其實係正常","createTime":"2019-02-21T13:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T17:58:25.000Z","uid":49616,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"937fb1f48ebd8f1a0308bb75f512910ecff1208b","tid":1031264,"uid":49616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"我知道係好多連登仔眼中 好多行都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實依d行業都係正常同必須，只係比某d唔專業既垃圾人渣做臭哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人做臭既例子<br />\n<br />\n1. 保險<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前線mk唔識野亂咁sell人呃人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾保險公司文化，洗腦式教育，明明想賺錢又乜柒扮到想幫人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果社會冇撚咗保險會好大獲，保險好大程度上保障咗好多打野（唔包括d垃圾呃人既保險）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後勤好多係專業人士，計保費 整保單等等。可惜佢地一樣會被定義為保險狗<br />\n<br />\n2. 老師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前終身制留咗班教畜，好多有心教既就比人迫走或者長期contract <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />部份人未夠班走去教中學，自己都唔撚識點教人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少部分低能人士成日叫春 做臭哂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多有心教，特別係後生既，可惜佢地多數係contract <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好老師真係會改變一個人一生，而且對社會好重要<br />\n<br />\n3. 社工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔專業既呃學生信任去報警 痴撚線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多學生真係有情緒困擾 真係要有社工幫助<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多社工係家暴、獨居老人等等問題上幫助好多，而且有定期搞活動 幫助社區融和<br />\n<br />\n真係仆街垃圾<br />\n<br />\n黑警<br />\n-大部分低學歷入去做，根本成行都係充斥住垃圾，睇下班休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府只係想要班聽教聽話既，愈無腦愈好<br />\n<br />\n倫敦金<br />\n- 解釋都廢事<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先<br />\n<br />\n同意就比個正皮黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b741fec4ff00ccc88b4cc914d53b89152c407e49","tid":1031264,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"地產代理<br />\n<br />\n其實好專業<br />\n<br />\n做事有熱誠<br />\n<br />\n為客人著想<br />\n<br />\n絕大部分都係高學歷<br />\n<br />\n有文化"},{"pid":"5f49c55c45c8d8a1b2e73354d833fe94cf15a167","tid":1031264,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"同意老師，其他唔同意"},{"pid":"da5636f1fb7bc211dfce420c139acad6132323d2","tid":1031264,"uid":49616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b741fec4ff00ccc88b4cc914d53b89152c407e49","tid":1031264,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"地產代理<br />\n<br />\n其實好專業<br />\n<br />\n做事有熱誠<br />\n<br />\n為客人著想<br />\n<br />\n絕大部分都係高學歷<br />\n<br />\n有文化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:01:57.000Z","msg":"Broker?"},{"pid":"1c3f352ae249222cdc6317dc572025ab6190f1ae","tid":1031264,"uid":49616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f49c55c45c8d8a1b2e73354d833fe94cf15a167","tid":1031264,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"同意老師，其他唔同意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:04:17.000Z","msg":"點唔同意法"},{"pid":"47da773ff8175c68c215455b240d18beb21fecfc","tid":1031264,"uid":49616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb311d9af95e3af905ccd75c63c91580f13878a","tid":1031264,"uid":134321,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87f3d8f5d0710cb74c924ce784d1179ac3b08e5f","tid":1031264,"uid":49616,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"